OL,3,CRise in number of children needing
OL,4,Ctreatment for severe mental health
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThere has been a rise in the number of
OL,8,Fchildren across England needing
OL,9,Fspecialist treatment for severe mental
OL,10,Fhealth crisis.
OL,12,FNHS data shows a 10% rise in
OL,13,Femergency, very urgent and urgent
OL,14,Freferrals for under-18s, to 34,793
OL,15,Fbetween April and October 2024, up
OL,16,Ffrom 31,749 in the same period the
OL,17,Fprevious year.
OL,19,FChildren requiring emergency care may
OL,20,Fbe suicidal or seriously ill as a
OL,21,Fresult of eating disorders.
