OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThose needing an urgent referral also
OL,8,Fneed to be seen quickly and could be
OL,9,Fat risk of serious harm.
OL,11,FThe data, analysed by the charity
OL,12,FYoungMinds for the PA news agency,
OL,13,Fshows there were 4,424 new "very
OL,14,Furgent referrals" to mental health
OL,15,Fcrisis care teams between April 2024
OL,16,Fand October 2024, up 13% from 3,912 in
OL,17,Fthe same period in the previous year.
