OL,7,FThere were also 24,886 new "urgent
OL,8,Freferrals" to crisis care teams
OL,9,Fbetween April and October, up 13% from
OL,10,F22,045 in the same period the year
OL,11,Fbefore.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, some 5,483 new "emergency
OL,14,Freferrals" to crisis care teams were
OL,15,Fmade between April and October, down
OL,16,F5% from 5,792.
OL,18,FPut together, the figures show a 10%
OL,19,Frise in all NHS urgent and emergency
OL,20,Fcare referrals across the period.
