OL,7,FData for October alone shows that new
OL,8,Freferrals to liaison psychiatry teams
OL,9,Ffrom A&E departments were up 4%, from
OL,10,F2,292 in October 2023 to 2,386 in
OL,11,FOctober 2024.
OL,13,FLiaison psychiatry teams are usually
OL,14,Fbased in hospitals and include
OL,15,Fpsychiatrists and mental health
OL,16,Fnurses, together with other staff such
OL,17,Fas psychologists, social workers and
OL,18,Foccupational therapists.
