OL,7,FLaura Bunt, chief executive at
OL,8,FYoungMinds, said: "Early support would
OL,9,Fhelp prevent many young people from
OL,10,Fbecoming more unwell, but instead
OL,11,Ftheir mental health is deteriorating,
OL,12,Fpushing them into crisis and, in some
OL,13,Finstances, putting young people's
OL,14,Flives at risk.
OL,16,F"This is a shocking betrayal of young
OL,17,Fpeople and their mental health.
