OL,7,F"Tweaks to the system will no longer
OL,8,Fwork. We need major reforms that
OL,9,Faddress the root causes of why so many
OL,10,Fyoung people are struggling."
OL,12,FDr Elaine Lockhart, chair of the Royal
OL,13,FCollege of Psychiatrists' child and
OL,14,Fadolescent faculty, said: "Mental
OL,15,Fhealth services help thousands of
OL,16,Fyoung people recover from mental ill-
OL,17,Fhealth every year but they're
OL,18,Fstruggling to manage soaring demand
OL,19,Fdue to staff shortages and a lack of
OL,20,Fresources.
