OL,7,F"This is contributing to longer
OL,8,Fwaiting lists and more young people
OL,9,Freaching a crisis point before they
OL,10,Fcan access the care they need."
OL,12,FDr Lockhart said pressures in the
OL,13,Fsystem meant there were challenges in
OL,14,Fretaining and recruiting staff.
OL,16,F"The government must provide frontline
OL,17,Fmental health services, including the
OL,18,Fmental health workforce, with the
OL,19,Fsupport and funding they need to treat
OL,20,Fyoung people in a timely manner," she
OL,21,Fadded.
